text: Tilde Maria Henny Märta Fröling (born May 15, 1980) is a Swedish television personality and actress. She is the daughter of actress Ewa Fröling. Fröling was born in Stockholm. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish actors Category:Swedish singers Category:Swedish television presenters Category:Reality television participants
